These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: asparagus, lemon
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, van
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the person eating asparagus is not to the right of the person driving the van##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | asparagus   | lemon   |
| Transport   | van | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, cola
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, swimming
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | cola | lemonade   |
| Sport      | swimming | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, cucumber
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, trance
1. the person eating cauliflower is not to the left of the fan of trance##8
2. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | cucumber | cauliflower |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | trance     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
